{"tid":1142416,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"偷2件UNIQLO衫　休班警圖自殺留醫未能應訊","createTime":"2019-05-07T05:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T05:29:04.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6bc83cff0b48119354ff42fbe8c0b214f37b8953","tid":1142416,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:09:38.000Z","msg":"一名休班男警昨日(6日)涉嫌在觀塘apm商場店舖偷竊2件總值128港元的衣服，其後接受警員查問時又涉不合作而被捕。他被控以一項盜竊及一項抗拒警務人員罪，原定今日(7日)由警車押解往觀塘法院提訊，惟控方指被告曾試圖自殺，現正留院，暫未能應訊。裁判官遂將案件暫時押後至5月10日提訊，若被告出院將提早帶到法庭應訊，押後期間被告繼續羈押。<br />\n<br />\n報稱警務人員的50歲被告劉志富，被控在今年5月6日於觀塘創紀之城第五期apm三樓一間店舖，偷竊一件價值49港元的白色童裝背心，及一件價值79港元的白色童裝T恤，合共總值128港元，上述物品為UNIQLO財產。劉另被控同日同地抗拒執行職責的警員陳志領。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190507/mobile/bkn-20190507112754940-0507_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190507%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190507112754940-0507_00822_001.html&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HKg2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=2e349e42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190507/mobile/bkn-20190507112754940-0507_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"50e2dd9575a84ad60425330147d1c6a00b15b5b7","tid":1142416,"uid":107364,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:10:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d8a80d670d3cb93cf68273ccb40f12e645400273","tid":1142416,"uid":168389,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:13:37.000Z","msg":"呀sir試衫唔使你教"},{"pid":"2394341f41282c9178dde62ca8f4cafcd3303486","tid":1142416,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:13:58.000Z","msg":"比起日本侵華呢啲碎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8319d9a1adc89deee6e4fca78b3f56f3a827ae58","tid":1142416,"uid":28195,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20110301/photo/0301-00176-021b4.jpg\" data-thumb